Package com.intellij.psi.tree

Interface ILazyParseableElementTypeBase

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IReparseableElementTypeBase
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EmbeddedLazyParseableElementType, GrBlockElementType, GrBlockLambdaBodyElementType, GrClosureElementType, GrCodeBlockElementType, GrConstructorBlockElementType, GroovyDocChameleonElementType, GroovyDocTagValueTokenType, GrStubFileElementType, HtmlFileElementType, ICodeFragmentElementType, IErrorCounterReparseableElementType, IFileElementType, IJShellElementType, ILazyParseableElementType, ILightStubFileElementType, IReparseableElementType, IStubFileElementType, JavaDocElementType.JavaDocLazyElementType, JavaElementType.ICodeBlockElementType, JavaElementType.JavaDummyElementType, JavaElementType.TypeTextElementType, JavaFileElementType, MarkdownLazyElementType, PyDocstringFileElementType, PyFileElementType, PyFunctionTypeAnnotationFileElementType, PyiFileElementType, RegExpFileElementType, RestPythonTemplateType, ShFileElementType, ShLazyBlockElementType, ShLazyDoBlockElementType, StubFileElementType, TemplateDataElementType, XmlElementType.EmbeddedHtmlContentElementType
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface ILazyParseableElementTypeBase
    An additional interface to be implemented by IElementType instances for tokens which should be parsed lazily, but for some reasons extending ILazyParseableElementType is impossible.
